name: Spongebob De-Quantize
author: joey
description:
Category: Anime and Cartoons
Purpose: Animation - Quantized

Removed color quantization/indexing and dithering from cartoon style images and textures
dataset: 1 frame from every scene of every episode of season 11 of Spongebob, downscaled 50% with nearest neighbor, then downscaled by 25% with box for the HR, then color quantized with 256 colors for the LR
